  "text": "The settings consisted of 70 color slides of within-forest environments containing no visible pathways. In addition, we made a conscious attempt to sample only the two within-forest settings of [CITATION_1] : high and low visual access. It was, therefore, a purposive sample of settings. Figure 2 provides examples of the two setting categories. No settings contained people. All were photographed in spring, summer, or early fall. All slides were oriented horizontally.",
